            "qualityStatement": {
                "standardsCompliance": {
                    "standard": {
                        "standardName": [
                            {
                                "lang": "fr",
                                "value": "Le codage des variables obligatoires et recommand\u00e9es est effectu\u00e9 en suivant les r\u00e8gles strictes \u00e9tablies par le r\u00e9seau FRANCIM et l\u2019ENCR. La topographie et la morphologie sont cod\u00e9es selon la Classification Internationale des Maladies pour l\u2019Oncologie 3\u00e8me \u00e9dition (CIM-O-3). Le stade au diagnostic (TNM) est cod\u00e9 selon l\u2019\u00e9dition de la classification de l\u2019Union Internationale Contre le Cancer (UICC) relative aux ann\u00e9es \u00e9tudi\u00e9es."
                            },
                            {
                                "lang": "en",
                                "value": "Coding for required and recommended variables is carried out by following the strict rules set down by FRANCIM network and ENCR. Topography and morphology are coded according to the International Classification of Diseases for Oncology, third edition (ICD-O-3). The stage at diagnosis (TNM) is coded according to the classification of the Union for International Cancer Control (UICC) concerning the years studied."
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                }
            },
